Known range. CHILE : Region IV (Coquimbo region): Elqui province: 11 Km N of Los Vilos. Region V (Valparaíso region). Petorca province: Zapallar ; Quebrada Huaquén, Pichicuy. Quilota province: La Campana National Park. Valparaíso province: Quebrada el Tigre, Cachagua. (See
